@startuml YTL_ROI_Business_Value
title YTL Cement - ROI & Annual Business Value
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5

rectangle "INVESTMENT REQUIRED" as investment #FFE6E6 {
  component [S/4HANA License\n(1 year): $200K-250K] as invest_license
  component [Infrastructure/Hardware:\n$150K-200K] as invest_infra
  component [Implementation Services\n(1,000 MD): $200K-300K] as invest_impl
  component [MVP Modules (5 modules):\n$160K-240K] as invest_mvp
  component [Change Management & Training:\n$100K-150K] as invest_training

  note right of investment
    **Total Phase 1 Investment: $810K-1,140K**
  end note
}

rectangle "ANNUAL BENEFITS (Year 1+)" as benefits #E6FFE6 {

  rectangle "BENEFIT 1: Invoice Matching" as b1 #CCFFCC {
    component [Volume: 28K invoices/month] as b1_vol
    component [Current loss: 1-2% mismatches] as b1_loss
    component [Undetected cost: $280K-560K] as b1_value
    component [Timeline: Month 4 onwards] as b1_timeline
  }

  rectangle "BENEFIT 2: GL Anomaly Detector" as b2 #CCFFCC {
    component [Labor: 2 FTE per close] as b2_labor
    component [Cost reduction: 4+ days saved] as b2_save
    component [Annual value: $192K] as b2_value
    component [Timeline: Month 4 onwards] as b2_timeline
  }

  rectangle "BENEFIT 3: Vendor Data Quality" as b3 #CCFFCC {
    component [Current: 23% duplicates] as b3_dup
    component [Volume: 8,000 vendors] as b3_vol
    component [Recovery: $200K-400K] as b3_value
    component [Timeline: Month 6 onwards] as b3_timeline
  }

  rectangle "BENEFIT 4: SoD Analyzer" as b4 #CCFFCC {
    component [Risk mitigation: No lag] as b4_risk
    component [Audit findings prevented] as b4_audit
    component [Labor savings: $40K] as b4_labor
    component [Timeline: Month 6 onwards] as b4_timeline
  }

  rectangle "BENEFIT 5: e-Invoice Module" as b5 #CCFFCC {
    component [Compliance: Q2 2026 deadline] as b5_compliance
    component [Labor savings: 0.5 FTE] as b5_labor
    component [Penalty avoidance: $X] as b5_penalty
    component [Timeline: Month 3 onwards] as b5_timeline
  }

  note bottom of benefits
    **Total Year 1 Benefit: $722K-1.2M**
    **Ongoing Annual Benefit (Year 2+): $722K-1.2M**
  end note
}

rectangle "ROI CALCULATION" as roi #FFFFCC {
  component [Year 1 Benefit: $722K-1.2M] as roi_ben
  component [Year 1 Cost: $1,000K] as roi_cost
  component [Net Benefit Year 1: -$278K to $200K] as roi_net
  component [Payback Period: 10-16 months] as roi_payback
  component [Year 2 Net: $722K-1.2M profit] as roi_year2

  note right of roi
    **3-Year ROI Projection:**

    Year 1: -$278K to $200K (investment phase)
    Year 2: +$722K-1.2M (payback complete, profit)
    Year 3: +$722K-1.2M (recurring benefit)

    **3-Year Total Net Benefit: $1.166M-2.1M**
    **IRR: 45-65% (Excellent)**
    **NPV @ 10%: $800K-1.5M (Strong)**
  end note
}

rectangle "INTANGIBLE BENEFITS (Non-Financial)" as intangible #E6E6FF {
  component [Operational Excellence:\nFaster GL close, automated processes] as int_ops
  component [Risk Reduction:\nReal-time compliance, SoD monitoring] as int_risk
  component [Data Quality:\nSingle source of truth] as int_data
  component [Future Flexibility:\nS/4HANA ready for cloud, AI, ML] as int_future
  component [Competitive Advantage:\nModern platform vs. 13-year legacy] as int_compete
}

note bottom
  **INVESTMENT JUSTIFICATION:**

  **Tangible ROI: 10-16 months (Strong Business Case)**
  - Every dollar invested returns $0.70-$1.20 in Year 1
  - Every dollar invested returns $0.70+ annually in Years 2+

  **Risk-Adjusted ROI:**
  - Even with 30% scope creep: 13-21 month payback
  - Even with 50% benefit realization: 20-32 month payback

  **Strategic Value:**
  - Compliance deadline (Q2 2026): Non-negotiable
  - Operational improvement: Foundation for future growth
  - Technical debt reduction: 100+ customizations -> MVP modules
  - Scalability: Ready for multi-plant rollout (Phase 3+)
end note

@enduml
